name: Whitstable Pyjamas
description: There’s something about bunting that never fails to make us smile. Cheery little flags fluttering in the wind reminds us of garden parties, sunny summer days and wandering down Whitstable High Street with an ice cream. These charming pyjamas will have you dreaming of warm summer day. Our Whitstable pyjamas are made from 100% soft, cool, light weight cotton with contrast piping on the collar, cuffs and breast pocket. The drawstring trousers have a gently elasticated back waist for extra comfort and the perfect fit. - 100% Cotton - 40°C Wash. Tumble dry low. Warm iron
